  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The researchers want to investigate the effects of muscle relaxation with rocuronium bromide
      during general anaesthesia on muscle trauma (serum CK, CRP) and postoperative analgesic
      consumption in patients with total hip prosthesis replacement (general vs. spinal
      anaesthesia).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
